# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Shiksha Intelligence Frontend — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your actual values.
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Backend (Spring Boot) ────────────────────────────────────────
# Used by the Vite dev-server proxy (vite.config.ts).
# You normally don't need to change this for local dev.
VITE_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:8080

# ── AI Server (Shiksha-Intelligence-AI-server) ───────────────────
# URL of the FastAPI AI service.
# Local dev: http://localhost:8001  (default — leave blank to use this)
# Production: https://your-ai-server.example.com
VITE_AI_SERVER_URL=http://localhost:8001
